divs: Sighting DetailsI was sitting outside, smoking, and noticed a light hovering in the same area of the sky as last report on May 31, 2009, however not as close this time as May 31, 2009. It stayed in the area moved slowly then headed off towards the Gulf. I did get 3 videos. Tried to upload them here however, it would not work.
Summary: UFO over Lacassine, not as close as last report on May 31, 2009, but in same area as seen then.
